title: Ep - 6 - Eric Nies of Real World New York Season 1
description:
Kate tracked down Eric Nies from the first season of Real World and chatted with Dana Weiss about Ben and Lauren: Happily Ever After, Wells Adams from The Bachelorette about an episode of Real Housewives of Orange County, and Anika Reitman about being a contestant on Catching Kelce.
